{"tid":2386080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葛珮帆支持電話卡實名制：我啲個人資料俾人拎咗去登記器官捐贈","createTime":"2021-01-29T11:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T03:12:47.000Z","uid":212626,"like":88,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"6243db83719ea7564f4391629935fc963e2b9c45","tid":2386080,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"葛珮帆又表示，很多人煽動青少年參與違法行為，手機有機會成為犯案工具，所以青少年使用電話時需要監護人登記是「比較合理」，讓他們知道網上行為亦須受法例規管。<br />\n<br />\n不過葛珮帆亦表示對實名制有「少少擔心」，因需要登記姓名、出生日期及身份證號碼，擔心只用以上資料，會有人偷取其他人的個人資料作登記。她以自己為例，已被人「起底」，出生日期及身份證號碼「差唔多係公開資訊」，擔心有人會以其資料登記「好多太空卡」，又提到曾被人以其個人資料登記器官捐贈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080518/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080518%2F&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=b78b8944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080518%2F&h=920fd15a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080518/</a>"},{"pid":"22d4ddac418d07f08399df5a7db72bd82a87f018","tid":2386080,"uid":312076,"like":188,"dislike":3,"score":185,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"你咁撚肥，登記都未必"},{"pid":"d012cc2692d02b2eeb532c1f0affbb3dff5f8072","tid":2386080,"uid":47697,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"算啦，登記咗器官捐贈都應該用唔著<br />\n無人要你啲器官啊割駁屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2837083e227921b40cb9ffca805b76525a8714fb","tid":2386080,"uid":169195,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"器官捐贈好事黎丫"},{"pid":"ffa65bd21b8a8c977404ae3d53692cd1258fa19d","tid":2386080,"uid":312076,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"22d4ddac418d07f08399df5a7db72bd82a87f018","tid":2386080,"uid":312076,"like":188,"dislike":3,"score":185,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"你咁撚肥，登記都未必"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:09:13.000Z",